				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$h(x,y)$$\end{document}h(x,y) and dispersal type, then estimated the density distribution using Gaussian kernel estimation. Finally, we determined the maximum point of the estimated density distribution as the estimated asymptotic growth rate.
